00:33.333 --> 00:34.375
Okay, you know what?

00:34.375 --> 00:36.417
Why don’t we write
that one in the car?

00:36.417 --> 00:37.709
-What? Oh.
-Okay, come on.

00:37.709 --> 00:39.166
